disc-080124.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/newjeans-danielle-ive-wonyoung-seventeen-joshua-golden-disc-080124-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/newjeans-danielle-ive-wonyoung-seventeen-joshua-golden-disc-080124-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/newjeans-danielle-ive-wonyoung-seventeen-joshua-golden-disc-080124-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/newjeans-danielle-ive-wonyoung-seventeen-joshua-golden-disc-080124-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/newjeans-danielle-ive-wonyoung-seventeen-joshua-golden-disc-080124-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>第 38 届金唱片奖于周末举行， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/seventeen">SEVENTEEN</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/newjeans">NewJeans</a>夺得当晚大奖 - 请查看下面的完整获奖者名单。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/best-k-pop-songs-of-the-year-2023-nme-3555798">2023 年 25 首最佳韩国流行歌曲</a></strong></li></ul><p>1月6日，第38届金唱片奖在印度尼西亚雅加达国际体育场举行。该颁奖典礼由成时京和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cha-eun-woo">车银优</a>主持，旨在表彰 2022 年 11 月中旬至 2023 年 11 月上旬发行的最佳韩国音乐。</p><p> SEVENTEEN 和 NewJeans 分别夺得年度专辑大奖和年度歌曲大奖，成为当晚的最大赢家。两位艺人与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ive">IVE</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bts">BTS</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jungkook">Jungkook</a>一起赢得了最佳专辑和歌曲类别的多项奖项，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stray-kids">Stray Kids</a>则被评为全球韩国流行艺人。</p><p>此次活动还进行了一系列表演，从<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/zerobaseone">ZEROBASEONE</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/boynextdoor">BOYNEXTDOOR</a>等韩国流行音乐新人到古典声乐团体 La Poem，后者表演了<a href="https://youtu.be/xtIivyAa-Ag?si=xSLpPfWyXt01gYvJ" target="_blank" rel="noopener">去年一些热门歌曲</a>的混合曲。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="[제38회 골든디스크] ZEROBASEONE (제로베 Been 스원) - &#39;Intro + In Bloom + Our Season&#39;♪｜JTBC 240106 방송" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/WWHi25dGu94?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="[제38회 골든디스크] BOYNEXTDOOR (보넥스트도어) - 《Serenade + 뭣 같아》♪｜JTBC 240106 방송" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/_lHUJjEqF5Q?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> SEVENTEEN 子团体 BSS 与乐队成员 Dino 一起<a href="https://youtu.be/0npT8GmirsQ?si=CpAsl_e3aOklM1dT" target="_blank" rel="noopener">表演了他们的热门单曲“Fighting”</a> ，随后全队表演了他们的 2023 年单曲“Super”和“God of Music”。 HYBE 男子乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/enhypen">ENHYPEN</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tomorrow-x-together">Tomorrow X Together</a>也表演了他们的一些最新曲目，后者的 Yeonjun 还<a href="https://youtu.be/hdh9OL_A1n0?si=eEsxzcjv4mTWmoG9" target="_blank" rel="noopener">翻唱了泰民的《Guilty》</a> 。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="[제38회 골든디스크] SEVENTEEN - &#39;손오공 + Ima -即使明天世界末日- + 음악의 신&#39; ♪｜JTBC 240106 방송" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/4sOX5bR4LYs?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="[제38회 골든디스크] ENHYPEN (엔하 Been) - ‘命运+咬我+甜蜜毒液’♪｜JTBC 240106 방송" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/RaOHX_R8JSQ?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="[제38회 골든디스크] TOMORROW X TOGETHER (투모로우바ֈ게더) - &#39;네버랜드를 떠나며 + 追逐那种感觉&#39;♪｜JTBC 240106 방송" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/EpLENCzqHNo?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>年度歌曲获得者 NewJeans 表演了他们的获奖单曲“Ditto”，以及他们最新迷你专辑“Get Up”中的“Cool With You”。实力女团IVE也带来了《Baddie》和《I Am》等热门歌曲。与此同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stayc">STAYC</a>表演了<a href="https://youtu.be/nfFgaoe4LxY?si=UJq5rzZLnB5sUyRS" target="_blank" rel="noopener">一系列标志性女子组合曲目</a>以及她们的单曲“Teddy Bear”和“Bubble”。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="[제38회 골든디스크] NewJeans (뉴진스) - &#39;Cool With You + Ditto&#39;♪｜JTBC 240106 방송" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/bbsZQ8x6i7U?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="[제38회 골든디스크] IVE (아브) - &#39;Intro + Baddie + Holy Moly + I AM&#39; ♪｜JTBC 240106 방송" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/WROkCS4UhSU?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>颁奖典礼主持人成诗京和车银优还合作了一首<a href="https://youtu.be/4CasrNjui_Q?si=HXzzqdjWvQ9ZAiyw" target="_blank" rel="noopener">特别的二重唱</a>，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/le-sserafim">LE SSERAFIM</a>则与韩国传奇摇滚乐队 YB 合作演唱了歌曲《Unforgiven》和《Fire in the Belly》。这位经验丰富的表演者后来<a href="https://youtu.be/XGeA5TDapio?si=NwTwYUNAulBmo8gS" target="_blank" rel="noopener">继续表演了</a>一些他们自己的热门歌曲。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="[제38회 골든디스크] YB X LE SSERAFIM - “UNFORGIVEN + Stay Alive + 腹中之火”♪｜JTBC 240106 방송" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/PbBW8awuQ6g?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>当晚的其他表演包括<a href="https://youtu.be/C5mphTU4kRM?si=U-2ILGcA6p4oEF-q" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Parc Jae-jung 的《Let&#39;s Say Goodbye》</a> ，以及<a href="https://y